    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "Well-kept vehicle in good overall condition and represented honestly. It shows the normal cosmetic wear you\u2019d expect for its age and use, including some minor exterior blemishes, light interior wear, and general signs of regular driving, but nothing out of line for a good used vehicle. It presents nicely, feels solid, and should be a good fit for someone looking for a dependable car without expecting a showroom-perfect example.",
