    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$18,900 - Honest, driver-quality classic in fair overall condition with a lot of appeal for someone who wants an affordable car to enjoy right away. It presents well enough to be proud of at a local cruise-in, while still showing the age and wear you\u2019d expect from a fair-condition example. A great choice for a buyer who values character, usability, and room to make it even better over time.",
