    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer who wants affordable transportation without a big upfront cost. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with an older vehicle, but it still offers solid value as an inexpensive daily driver, backup car, or light project. Priced to move, this is a straightforward opportunity to get into a vehicle at a very accessible price point.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone handy, a first-time buyer needing basic transport, or anyone after a project to tinker with. It\u2019s being sold honestly as a used vehicle with wear and age showing, but it still offers a lot of value for the money. If you want something inexpensive and approachable without spending a fortune, this could be a smart little buy.",
      "price": 3950.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or workhorse with a strong-running engine, dependable drivetrain engagement, and plenty of usable life for the right owner. Cosmetically rough around the edges and shows its age, but it still offers good road manners, a straightforward mechanical layout, and the kind of platform that\u2019s easy to sort, drive, and improve over time. Great candidate for a daily beater, shop runner, or enthusiast project if you want something affordable with real utility.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car today. Rough around the edges, priced to move fast.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Not every vehicle is about perfection\u2014some are about possibility. This one has the kind of honest, hard-earned character that tells a story the moment you see it. It\u2019s the sort of car that feels right at home with someone who appreciates grit, style, and a machine that still has more to give. Whether you\u2019re after an affordable set of wheels, a practical runabout, or a project with personality, this car offers a chance to make it your own without breaking the bank. A budget-friendly entry with unmistakable presence and plenty of potential for its next chapter.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
